modules.description: Provides a function to configure a real-time axis for time-based charts, using a specific time axis type. Works with the Chartjs.timeAxis type and related axis configuration structures. Used to dynamically update chart axes with live data timestamps.

Provides functions to generate and configure horizontal bar charts, including data series, axis labels, and styling options. Works with OCaml lists and custom record types representing chart configurations and dataset values. Used to embed interactive charts in web applications with dynamic data visualization requirements.
